here a tactic for getting &nbsp;one of the parts &nbsp;of the item... <br> <br>Lord Neh'Ashiir...same guy that is sposed to have our Torch of Elements  <br>Afierra Lonecaster Elementalist Nightmare Clan <br> <br>  <br>Quix <br>Mage <br>(10/20/00 8:37:00 pm) <br>Reply Re: Runed ornate shield <br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>Yes, it RoS is from Neh in Com. Is cake to get. Need one group w/ rogue. Some creative thinking and a lil gflux will save you ALOT of time. Have done it several time and taken up to 8 reavers at one time + Neh. Hope this helps. <br> <br>BTW. He does drop torch of elements. Got mine awhile back. <br> <br>-Quixor <br> <br>Brotherhood of the Spider <br>www.drow.org <br>The Rathe  <br> <br>Edited by: Quix at: 10/20/00 8:37:00 pm <br> <br>  <br>Dristan &nbsp; <br>Mage <br>(10/21/00 4:53:49 pm) <br>Reply <br> Re: Runed ornate shield <br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>you have got me curious what do you mean with the creative and the gflux?  <br>Dristan Bloodmoon <br> <br>The Unbidden <br> <br>Dristan says,&quot;Pet Kill!&quot; <br>Gobartik says,&quot; yes master.&quot; <br>Dristan says,&quot;Pet back off!&quot; <br>Gobartik says,&quot;I can't master he's hitting me!&quot;  <br>Dristan says,&quot;If you don't get this one off ME you aren't gonna be around long enough to kill that one that is hitting you!&quot; <br>Gobartik says,&quot;Mob hitting me can't follow orders sir.&quot; <br>Dristan says,&quot;Fine get lost then! What i wouldn't give for a pet ignore attacker command!&quot;  <br> <br>  <br>Rulan &nbsp; <br>Mage <br>(10/23/00 1:48:35 am) <br>Reply <br> Re: Runed ornate shield <br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>8 reavers + Neh with one group? Are you god?  <br>Rulan Thomatrem <br>Alliance of the Light <br> <br>  <br>Ailees &nbsp; <br>Elementalist <br>(10/23/00 9:39:53 am) <br>Reply <br> Re: Runed ornate shield <br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>&gt;&gt;Some creative thinking and a lil gflux will save you ALOT of time <br> <br>what does that mean ? I agree are you a god, or just you want us to give 254 messages before answering ? <br>  <br> <br>  <br>Lorendel Daywalker &nbsp; <br>Elementalist <br>(10/23/00 9:47:38 am) <br>Reply <br> Re: Runed ornate shield <br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>Just my 2cp, but maybe he meant this: give everyone a ring of levitation, then have the enchanter gravity flux everyone, as soon as you get high enough, use the lev ring to stay there, then run onto a skybridge, use the rogue to pick the lock to Neh'Ashiir's place. <br> <br>Dunno if i'd try that personally, sounds way too dicey, but I suppose it's theoretically possible. I think it's more fun to fight my way there. &nbsp; <br> <br>Might try the timing thing with a enchanter buddy to see if it's even possible... <br> <br>Lorendel Daywalker <br>44th Mage of the Mithril Heart Brigade <br>The Tribunal  <br> <br>  <br>AutumnSkyfire &nbsp; <br>Mage <br>(10/23/00 12:01:45 pm) <br>Reply Re: Runed ornate shield <br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>Goo and skeleton's roam the pathways to Sky Tower. If you grav flux then lev at max height, most likely would get some monsters next to you. Would be tough to get 1 person up there without aggro, let alone 6. <br> <br>Autumn  <br> <br>  <br>Quix <br>Mage <br>(10/24/00 2:48:02 pm) <br>Reply Re: Runed ornate shield <br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>Group of 6: <br> <br>1 mage <br>1 enchater <br>1 rogue <br>1 wiz <br>1 cleric <br>1 warrior <br> <br>Have the enchanter lead the group. Hotkey a lev ring for quick use, duel the chanter, have him gflux you up to the walkway above the first gate. Don't lev yourself until your at the maximum height of the glux, otherwise your lev height will be decreased by half. If there is a mob there, simply float down, clear agro, and try again after a few minutes. As soon as your up there, summon him up. After your both up, log quickly so you cancel the duel and are able to summon your other group members. Then its only a short trip of to Neh's crib.  <br> <br>At this point, its just a matter of how good your group can own. We have done it w/ a full group of 6 w/ only a ranger as a tank and taken like 4/5 reavs. <br> <br> <br>-Quixor <br> <br>Brotherhood of the Spider <br>www.drow.org <br>The Rathe <br> <br> <br>  <br>Lilgirlx23 <br>Mage <br>(10/30/00 12:06:56 am) <br>Reply Re: Runed ornate shield <br>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <br>easiest way, grav flux mage up, have the leader stay at zone line for invites and just us our spell Call of the Heores, all members will be rolling with no  <br>
